title: Design arrangements for US-bound air cargo security (Department of Infrastructure and Regional Development - Australian ...
text: ( Source : Department of Infrastructure and Regional Development - Australian Government ) The United States (US) obliges all airlines transporting air cargo to the US on a passenger flight to examine 100 per cent of air cargo at piece-level.
